Packages
suncertify This package contains classes related to the URLyBird program that do not belong in any particular package.
suncertify.client This package contains classes for the URLyBird client, including model, view and controller classes.
suncertify.db This package contains classes related to the database back end.
suncertify.fields This package contains classes for representing database fields.
suncertify.fields.parsers This package contains classes for parsing strings in a database file into fields, and converting fields into strings suitable to be written to a database file.
suncertify.fields.viewers This package contains classes for obtaining information about how to display fields.
suncertify.panels This package contains various GUI panels and widgets used in the URLyBird client and server.
suncertify.server This package contains high-level classes for the URLyBird server, including model, view and controller classes.
suncertify.utils This package contains highly reusable classes that may be useful to other programs besides URLyBird.
